                  <div class="flex justify-end gap-2">
                    <div class="max-w-xs rounded-2xl rounded-tr-none bg-[color:var(--color-ink)] px-3 py-2 text-[13px] text-white">
                      "Saw your post Maya, built Typpout for exactly this. 5-min call on what we see in Pulse's space?"
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex items-center justify-between text-[11px] text-[color:var(--color-ink-muted)]">
                    <span class="font-mono">AI-generated in 0:00:08</span>
